          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-lime/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium text-dark-green">A</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-medium">Anisa R.</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Shopee</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card shrink-0 w-[300px] bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            <span class="text-lime text-sm">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">"keychainnya super cute dan kualitasnya oke. acrylic-nya tebal, gambarnya jelas. packing juga rapi. recommended!"</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-pink/50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium text-dark-green">D</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-medium">Dinda S.</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Shopee</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card shrink-0 w-[300px] bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            <span class="text-lime text-sm">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">"the stickers are so pretty! perfect for journaling. the vinyl quality is great and they're waterproof as described."</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-lime/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium text-dark-green">M</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-medium">Mei L.</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Shopee</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card shrink-0 w-[300px] bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            <span class="text-lime text-sm">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">"griptok-nya gemesin banget! 3M adhesive-nya juga kuat, udah sebulan dipake dan gak lepas. love it!"</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-pink/50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium text-dark-green">F</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-medium">Fitri N.</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Shopee</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card shrink-0 w-[300px] bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            <span class="text-lime text-sm">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">"bought these for my bullet journal and they're perfect! the designs are unique and the kiss cut makes them so easy to peel."</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-lime/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium text-dark-green">S</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-medium">Sarah K.</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Shopee</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card shrink-0 w-[300px] bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            <span class="text-lime text-sm">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">"artprint-nya kecil tapi detailnya bagus banget. kertas linen-nya juga premium. cocok buat hadiah!"</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-pink/50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium text-dark-green">R</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-medium">Rina W.</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Shopee</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card shrink-0 w-[300px] bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            <span class="text-lime text-sm">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">"i keep coming back to this shop. every design is so cute and thoughtful. the alphabet sticker sheets are my absolute favorite!"</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-lime/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium text-dark-green">J</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-medium">Jasmine T.</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Shopee</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card shrink-0 w-[300px] bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            <span class="text-lime text-sm">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">"pengiriman cepat, packing aman banget. sticker sheet-nya lucu-lucu, anak saya suka banget. pasti order lagi!"</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-pink/50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium text-dark-green">L</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-medium">Lisa M.</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Shopee</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="review-card shrink-0 w-[300px] bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-3">
            <span class="text-lime text-sm">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">"ordered from japan and it arrived quickly. amazing quality stickers, very vibrant colors. will order more for gifts!"</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-lime/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-medium text-dark-green">Y</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-medium">Yuki H.</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">International</p>
            </div>
